reviewText: What's not to love? Sure Mary Martin is no Judy Holliday,  but she Judy's Brock and Devery, she even has Arthur Hill as her Paul. Plus Garson Lenin, the author. Is the director of this production.  Hallmark Hall of Fame 1956! This is great if you are a fan of Born Yesterday.
I love the Judy Holiday movie version but this TV version is just as enjoyable and very cool for the original golden age of live TV.
